[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "どうしたのさ……こんな夜更けの港に呼び出すなんて。\nまさか告白とか、そういうセンもあったりする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01393",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "ある意味ではそうかもしれんな。\nジョゼ・ダンブロシオ。お前の力を借りたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01394",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "また監察官になれって話？\n悪いけど、それだけは何度言われても無理だね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01395",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや、今回は少し違う。\n賞金稼ぎとして協力してほしいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01396",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おっ。少しは俺の生き方に譲歩してくれたんだ。\nそれで、あんたらに協力して俺になんの得が？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01397",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "もしかして、オイタしても見逃してくれるとか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01398",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "そんなわけがないだろう。オイタをしたら叱る",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01399",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "だよね。むしろそうでないと寂しいよ、\n張り合いがなくて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01400",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ついでに聞くけどさ、向こうに人を置いてるのは\n俺が拒否したら無理矢理拘束するため？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01401",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "いや、彼女たちもお前に言いたいことがあるそうだ。\nモテるな、お前",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01402",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "まぁ仮面で個性を出してるからね。結構モテるよ。\nただ――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01403",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おっかなそうな連中にモテるのは、考えものだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01404",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "なんだ、旅の終わりに知った顔が出迎えか？\n気が利くじゃないか。土産はないがな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01405",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ヘルト、ゼロ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_01406",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "駆け付けてくるとは感心だ。話が早くていい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01407",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "うぬらの言う通り、世界を見て回ってきてやったぞ。\nなかなか退屈しない旅じゃったわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01408",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……どうだった？　今の人間自身が管理する世界は",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01409",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "端的に言って、健気だな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01410",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "それぞれが懸命に、その日を生きている。\nその姿は美しくて、それでいて弱くて儚い",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01411",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "か弱い花はより上位の存在である我らが「管理」して\n育ててやらねばならぬ！　そう思ったのじゃ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01412",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "やっぱりそういう結論になったのね。\nなんでもベスティラにもちょっかいかけたそうじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01413",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ああ、あそこは「管理」が必要な国の典型だ。\n力不足の癖に、己の腕っぷしを頼みにしている",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01414",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ああいう連中には絶対的な上位存在を分からせんとな。\nもう少し謙虚に生きてもらいたいもんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01415",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "結局、さらなる力で統治するってことですか？\n納得いきません！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01416",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "人類の上位者を名乗る者の統治など\n生憎と望んでいない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_01417",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "やたら突っかかるじゃないか。\n俺はむしろ「管理」してやると言っているのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01418",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺たち上位存在の力が無用だと言うなら、\nそれ相応の力を見せてみることだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01419",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あれは……「九偉人図」、それも２枚も！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01420",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "お前たちはこれを探していたのだろう？\n九偉人図……もう少し似せて描いてもらいたかったなぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01421",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "旅先で見つけたついでに保護してやったのじゃ。\n欲しければ、力ずくで奪ってみるがよい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01422",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "力が見たけりゃ見せてやるわよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01423",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "その代わりこっちが勝ったらその九偉人図をもらうわ！\nあと、キューンとか兄弟への接し方も改めて！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01424",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "注文が多い妹だな……だが、それくらい\nわがままなほうが手が掛かってかわいいというもの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01425",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そっちが世界旅行してる間にね、こっちだって\nただ待ってたわけじゃない。腕を上げたのよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01426",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "それでは見せてもらうか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01427",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01428",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01429",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ふむ、本当に腕は上げたようだし、\n俺への備えも十分といった様子だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01430",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "我らと戦う最低限の資格はあるようじゃの。\n久方ぶりに楽しめそうじゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_01431",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "チッ……なんて迫力だ……\nこいつら、まさかこのままここでやり合う気か……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_01432",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]